{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775889359245,"sessionID":"ses_284bf8cc4ffepOzrBWJCfD7y2y","part":{"id":"prt_d7b412169001vJNPzy0LKVnpzN","messageID":"msg_d7b410c3f001Lv09hh0wGcmRFq","sessionID":"ses_284bf8cc4ffepOzrBWJCfD7y2y","type":"tool","tool":"read","callID":"toolu_tool-6feb6b6c532f440eb885a8f56d3a17d4","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20260410T163124Z/changes/AR-034/design.md"},"output":"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20260410T163124Z/changes/AR-034/design.md</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>\n1: # AR-034 — CI/CD GitHub Actions Design\n2: \n3: ## Overview\n4: \n5: | Item | Value |\n6: |------|-------|\n7: | AR | AR-034 — CI/CD GitHub Actions (12 workflows) |\n8: | Module | `.github` |\n9: | Language | YAML |\n10: | Size | L |\n11: | Stage | ST-1 (completed) |\n12: \n13: ---\n14: \n15: ## Architecture\n16: \n17: ### High-Level CI/CD Pipeline Flow\n18: \n19: ```\n20: ┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐\n21: │                         GitHub Actions CI/CD Pipeline                            │\n22: ├─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┤\n23: │                                                                                  │\n24: │  ┌──────────────┐                                                                │\n25: │  │ Pull Request │                                                                │\n26: │  │  to main     │                                                                │\n27: │  └──────────────┘                                                                │\n28: │         │                                                                        │\n29: │         ▼                                                                        │\n30: │  ┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐│\n31: │  │                    Triggered Workflows (Parallel)                           ││\n32: │  ├─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┤│\n33: │  │                                                                              ││\n34: │  │  ┌──────────────┐ ┌──────────────┐ ┌──────────────┐ ┌────────────────────┐ ││\n35: │  │  │   main.yml   │ │   e2e.yml    │ │   lint.yml   │ │ test-coverage.yml  │ ││\n36: │  │  │ Docker Build │ │ E2E on Kind  │ │ Go golangci  │ │ Go test + coverage │ ││\n37: │  │  └──────────────┘ └──────────────┘ └──────────────┘ └────────────────────┘ ││\n38: │  │                                                                              ││\n39: │  │  ┌──────────────┐ ┌──────────────┐ ┌──────────────┐ ┌────────────────────┐ ││\n40: │  │  │ python-sdk-  │ │ python-lint  │ │ codegen-     │ │ copyright-check.yml│ ││\n41: │  │  │ tests.yml    │ │ .yml (Ruff)  │ │ check.yml    │ │ Copyright headers  │ ││\n42: │  │  └──────────────┘ └──────────────┘ └──────────────┘ └────────────────────┘ ││\n43: │  │                                                                              ││\n44: │  │  ┌──────────────────┐                                                        ││\n45: │  │  │   codespell.yml   │                                                        ││\n46: │  │  │ Spelling check    │                                                        ││\n47: │  │  └──────────────────┘                                                        ││\n48: │  │                                                                              ││\n49: │  └─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘│\n50: │                                                                                  │\n51: │  ┌──────────────┐                                                                │\n52: │  │ Push to main │                                                                │\n53: │  │ or v* tag    │                                                                │\n54: │  └──────────────┘                                                                │\n55: │         │                                                                        │\n56: │         ▼                                                                        │\n57: │  ┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐│\n58: │  │                                                                              ││\n59: │  │  ┌───────────────────────┐                                                  ││\n60: │  │  │ build-push-release.yml │                                                  ││\n61: │  │  │ Build + Push to ghcr.io│                                                  ││\n62: │  │  │ (workloadmanager,      │                                                  ││\n63: │  │  │  router, picod)        │                                                  ││\n64: │  │  └───────────────────────┘                                                  ││\n65: │  │                                                                              ││\n66: │  └─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘│\n67: │                                                                                  │\n68: │  ┌───────────────────┐                                                           │\n69: │  │ Push tag          │                                                           │\n70: │  │ dify-plugin/v*    │                                                           │\n71: │  └───────────────────┘                                                           │\n72: │         │                                                                        │\n73: │         ▼                                                                        │\n74: │  ┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐│\n75: │  │                                                                              ││\n76: │  │  ┌───────────────────────────┐                                              ││\n77: │  │  │ dify-plugin-publish.yml    │                                              ││\n78: │  │  │ Package + PR to            │                                              ││\n79: │  │  │ langgenius/dify-plugins    │                                              ││\n80: │  │  └───────────────────────────┘                                              ││\n81: │  │                                                                              ││\n82: │  └─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘│\n83: │                                                                                  │\n84: │  ┌───────────────────────────────┐                                               │\n85: │  │ pull_request_target           │                                               │\n86: │  │ (labeled, synchronize)        │                                               │\n87: │  └───────────────────────────────┘                                               │\n88: │         │                                                                        │\n89: │         ▼                                                                        │\n90: │  ┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐│\n91: │  │                                                                              ││\n92: │  │  ┌───────────────────────────────┐                                          ││\n93: │  │  │ workflows-approve.yml          │                                          ││\n94: │  │  │ Auto-approve for trusted       │                                          ││\n95: │  │  │ contributors or ok-to-test     │                                          ││\n96: │  │  └───────────────────────────────┘                                          ││\n97: │  │                                                                              ││\n98: │  └─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘│\n99: │                                                                                  │\n100: └─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘\n101: ```\n102: \n103: ### Workflow Dependency Graph\n104: \n105: ```\n106:                     ┌─────────────────────┐\n107:                     │    Repository       │\n108:                     │  (agentcube repo)   │\n109:                     └─────────────────────┘\n110:                               │\n111:            ┌──────────────────┼──────────────────┐\n112:            │                  │                  │\n113:            ▼                  ▼                  ▼\n114: ┌──────────────────┐ ┌──────────────────┐ ┌──────────────────┐\n115: │   Makefile       │ │   test/e2e/      │ │   sdk-python/    │\n116: │   Targets:       │ │   run_e2e.sh     │ │   pytest tests   │\n117: │   - docker-build │ │   fixtures       │ │                  │\n118: │   - lint         │ │                  │ │                  │\n119: │   - gen-check    │ │                  │ │                  │\n120: │   - e2e          │ │                  │ │                  │\n121: └──────────────────┘ └──────────────────┘ └──────────────────┘\n122:            │                  │                  │\n123:            │                  │                  │\n124:            ▼                  ▼                  ▼\n125: ┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐\n126: │                    GitHub Actions                            │\n127: │  ┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐│\n128: │  │ Workflows consume external resources:                   ││\n129: │  │ - actions/checkout@v4                                   ││\n130: │  │ - actions/setup-go@v5                                   ││\n131: │  │ - actions/setup-python@v5                               ││\n132: │  │ - docker/setup-buildx-action@v3                         ││\n133: │  │ - docker/login-action@v3                                ││\n134: │  │ - helm/kind-action@v1                                   ││\n135: │  │ - dorny/paths-filter@v3                                 ││\n136: │  │ - codecov/codecov-action@v4                             ││\n137: │  │ - actions/github-script@v7                              ││\n138: │  └─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘│\n139: └─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘\n140: ```\n141: \n142: ### Component Relationships\n143: \n144: ```\n145: ┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐\n146: │                      Workflow-to-Makefile Mapping                            │\n147: ├─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┤\n148: │                                                                              │\n149: │  Workflow                  Makefile Target        Build Output               │\n150: │  ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────  │\n151: │                                                                              │\n152: │  main.yml                  docker-build          workloadmanager:latest      │\n153: │                                                                              │\n154: │  e2e.yml                   docker-build          workloadmanager:latest      │\n155: │                            docker-build-router   agentcube-router:latest     │\n156: │                            docker-build-picod    picod:latest                │\n157: │                            e2e                   —                           │\n158: │                            e2e-clean             —                           │\n159: │                                                                              │\n160: │  lint.yml                  lint                  —                           │\n161: │                                                                              │\n162: │  test-coverage.yml         go test               coverage.out                │\n163: │                                                                              │\n164: │  codegen-check.yml         gen-check             —                           │\n165: │                                                                              │\n166: │  copyright-check.yml       gen-copyright         —                           │\n167: │                                                                              │\n168: │  build-push-release.yml    docker-buildx-push    workloadmanager:${TAG}      │\n169: │                            docker-buildx-push-   agentcube-router:${TAG}      │\n170: │                              router                                             │\n171: │                            docker-buildx-push-   picod:${TAG}                 │\n172: │                              picod                                              │\n173: │                                                                              │\n174: └─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘\n175: ```\n176: \n177: ---\n178: \n179: ## Data Structures\n180: \n181: ### Workflow YAML Structure\n182: \n183: Each workflow follows this canonical structure:\n184: \n185: ```yaml\n186: name: \"<Descriptive Workflow Name>\"\n187: on:\n188:   <trigger-specification>\n189: \n190: jobs:\n191:   <job-name>:\n192:     runs-on: ubuntu-latest\n193:     if: <conditional-expression>\n194:     steps:\n195:       - name: \"<Step Description>\"\n196:         uses: <action-reference>\n197:         with:\n198:           <action-inputs>\n199:         env:\n200:           <environment-variables>\n201: ```\n202: \n203: ### Path Filter Definitions\n204: \n205: ```yaml\n206: filters:\n207:   lint:\n208:     - '**/*.go'\n209:     - 'go.mod'\n210:     - 'go.sum'\n211:     - '.golangci.yml'\n212:     - '.github/workflows/lint.yml'\n213:   \n214:   sdk:\n215:     - 'sdk-python/**'\n216:   \n217:   python:\n218:     - 'cmd/cli/**'\n219:     - 'sdk-python/**'\n220:     - 'example/**'\n221:     - 'test/**/*.py'\n222:     - 'pyproject.toml'\n223:     - '.github/workflows/python-lint.yml'\n224:   \n225:   coverage:\n226:     - '**'\n227:     - '!*.md'\n228:     - '!*.svg'\n229:     - '!*.png'\n230:   \n231:   codegen:\n232:     - 'pkg/apis/**'\n233:     - 'hack/**'\n234:     - '.github/workflows/**'\n235:     - 'Makefile'\n236:   \n237:   copyright:\n238:     - '**'\n239:     - '!*.md'\n240:     - '!*.svg'\n241:     - '!*.png'\n242:     - '!docs/**'\n243:     - '!.github/**'\n244: ```\n245: \n246: ### Workflow Output Variables\n247: \n248: ```yaml\n249: outputs:\n250:   lint-changed: ${{ steps.filter.outputs.lint }}\n251:   sdk-changed: ${{ steps.filter.outputs.sdk }}\n252:   python-changed: ${{ steps.filter.outputs.python }}\n253:   coverage-changed: ${{ steps.filter.outputs.coverage }}\n254:   codegen-changed: ${{ steps.filter.outputs.codegen }}\n255:   copyright-changed: ${{ steps.filter.outputs.copyright }}\n256: ```\n257: \n258: ### Artifact Specifications\n259: \n260: ```yaml\n261: artifacts:\n262:   go-coverage:\n263:     path: coverage.out\n264:     retention-days: 7\n265:     \n266:   e2e-logs:\n267:     path: e2e-logs/\n268:     retention-days: 7\n269:     if-no-files-found: warn\n270: ```\n271: \n272: ### Environment Variable Contract\n273: \n274: ```yaml\n275: env:\n276:   ARTIFACTS_PATH: ${{ github.workspace }}/e2e-logs\n277:   TAG: ${{ github.ref_type == 'tag' && github.ref_name || 'latest' }}\n278:   IMAGE_REGISTRY: ghcr.io/${{ github.repository_owner }}\n279:   WORKLOAD_MANAGER_IMAGE: workloadmanager:${{ env.TAG }}\n280:   ROUTER_IMAGE: agentcube-router:${{ env.TAG }}\n281:   PICOD_IMAGE: picod:${{ env.TAG }}\n282:   AGENTCUBE_NAMESPACE: agentcube\n283:   WORKLOAD_MANAGER_URL: http://localhost:${{ env.WORKLOAD_MANAGER_LOCAL_PORT }}\n284:   ROUTER_URL: http://localhost:${{ env.ROUTER_LOCAL_PORT }}\n285: ```\n286: \n287: ---\n288: \n289: ## API Contracts\n290: \n291: ### Workflow Trigger Specification\n292: \n293: ```yaml\n294: on:\n295:   pull_request:\n296:     branches:\n297:       - main\n298:       - 'release-*'\n299:     types:\n300:       - opened\n301:       - synchronize\n302:       - reopened\n303:   \n304:   push:\n305:     branches:\n306:       - main\n307:     tags:\n308:       - 'v*.*.*'\n309:       - 'v*.*.*-*'\n310:       - 'dify-plugin/v*'\n311:   \n312:   merge_group:\n313:   \n314:   workflow_call:\n315:     inputs:\n316:       CODECOV_TOKEN:\n317:         description: 'Codecov upload token'\n318:         required: false\n319:         type: string\n320:     secrets:\n321:       CODECOV_TOKEN:\n322:         description: 'Codecov token for coverage upload'\n323:         required: false\n324:   \n325:   pull_request_target:\n326:     branches:\n327:       - main\n328:       - 'release-**'\n329:     types:\n330:       - labeled\n331:       - synchronize\n332: ```\n333: \n334: ### GitHub Actions API Contract\n335: \n336: ```yaml\n337: actions_api:\n338:   checkout:\n339:     uses: actions/checkout@v4\n340:     with:\n341:       fetch-depth: 0\n342:   \n343:   setup_go:\n344:     uses: actions/setup-go@v5\n345:     with:\n346:       go-version: '1.24'\n347:       cache: true\n348:   \n349:   setup_go_123:\n350:     uses: actions/setup-go@v5\n351:     with:\n352:       go-version: '1.23'\n353:       cache: true\n354:   \n355:   setup_go_1244:\n356:     uses: actions/setup-go@v5\n357:     with:\n358:       go-version: '1.24.4'\n359:       cache: true\n360:   \n361:   setup_python:\n362:     uses: actions/setup-python@v5\n363:     with:\n364:       python-version: '3.12'\n365:       cache: pip\n366:   \n367:   setup_python_310:\n368:     uses: actions/setup-python@v5\n369:     with:\n370:       python-version: '3.10'\n371:       cache: pip\n372:   \n373:   setup_buildx:\n374:     uses: docker/setup-buildx-action@v3\n375:   \n376:   docker_login:\n377:     uses: docker/login-action@v3\n378:     with:\n379:       registry: ghcr.io\n380:       username: ${{ github.actor }}\n381:       password: ${{ secrets.GITHUB_TOKEN }}\n382:   \n383:   paths_filter:\n384:     uses: dorny/paths-filter@v3\n385:     with:\n386:       filters: .github/workflows/filters.yaml\n387:   \n388:   kind_action:\n389:     uses: helm/kind-action@v1\n390:     with:\n391:       install_only: true\n392:       version: v0.30.0\n393:   \n394:   codecov:\n395:     uses: codecov/codecov-action@v4\n396:     with:\n397:       file: coverage.out\n398:       fail_ci_if_error: false\n399:       token: ${{ secrets.CODECOV_TOKEN }}\n400:   \n401:   github_script:\n402:     uses: actions/github-script@v7\n403:     with:\n404:       script: |\n405:         <inline-script>\n406: ```\n407: \n408: ### Makefile Target Contract\n409: \n410: ```yaml\n411: makefile_targets:\n412:   docker-build:\n413:     description: Build workload manager Docker image\n414:     prerequisites: Docker, Buildx\n415:     output: workloadmanager:latest\n416:     \n417:   docker-build-router:\n418:     description: Build router Docker image\n419:     prerequisites: Docker, Buildx\n420:     output: agentcube-router:latest\n421:     \n422:   docker-build-picod:\n423:     description: Build picod Docker image\n424:     prerequisites: Docker, Buildx\n425:     output: picod:latest\n426:     \n427:   docker-buildx-push:\n428:     description: Push workload manager to registry\n429:     env_vars:\n430:       - IMAGE_REGISTRY\n431:       - WORKLOAD_MANAGER_IMAGE\n432:     prerequisites: docker/login-action\n433:     \n434:   docker-buildx-push-router:\n435:     description: Push router to registry\n436:     env_vars:\n437:       - IMAGE_REGISTRY\n438:       - ROUTER_IMAGE\n439:     prerequisites: docker/login-action\n440:     \n441:   docker-buildx-push-picod:\n442:     description: Push picod to registry\n443:     env_vars:\n444:       - IMAGE_REGISTRY\n445:       - PICOD_IMAGE\n446:     prerequisites: docker/login-action\n447:     \n448:   lint:\n449:     description: Run golangci-lint\n450:     prerequisites: Go 1.24, .golangci.yml\n451:     \n452:   gen-check:\n453:     description: Verify generated code matches committed version\n454:     command_sequence:\n455:       - make gen-all\n456:       - git diff --exit-code\n457:     prerequisites: Go 1.24.4\n458:     \n459:   gen-copyright:\n460:     description: Generate copyright headers\n461:     prerequisites: moreutils (sponge)\n462:     \n463:   e2e:\n464:     description: Run E2E tests\n465:     prerequisites: Kind v0.30.0, Go 1.23, agent-sandbox CRDs\n466:     \n467:   e2e-clean:\n468:     description: Cleanup E2E resources\n469:     command: kind delete cluster --name agentcube-e2e\n470: ```\n471: \n472: ### Kind Cluster Configuration\n473: \n474: ```yaml\n475: kind_cluster:\n476:   name: agentcube-e2e\n477:   version: v0.30.0\n478:   \n479:   images_loaded:\n480:     - registry.k8s.io/agent-sandbox/agent-sandbox-controller:v0.1.1\n481:     - python:3.9-slim\n482:     - workloadmanager:latest\n483:     - agentcube-router:latest\n484:     - picod:latest\n485:     - redis:7-alpine\n486:   \n487:   crds_applied:\n488:     - https://github.com/kubernetes-sigs/agent-sandbox/releases/download/v0.1.1/manifest.yaml\n489:     - https://github.com/kubernetes-sigs/agent-sandbox/releases/download/v0.1.1/extensions.yaml\n490:   \n491:   helm_chart:\n492:     path: manifests/charts/base\n493:     release: agentcube\n494:     namespace: agentcube\n495:     values:\n496:       redis.address: redis.agentcube.svc.cluster.local:6379\n497:       redis.password: \"\"\n498:       workloadmanager.image.repository: workloadmanager\n499:       workloadmanager.image.tag: latest\n500:       router.image.repository: agentcube-router\n501:       router.image.tag: latest\n502:       router.rbac.create: true\n503:       router.serviceAccountName: agentcube-router\n504: ```\n505: \n506: ---\n507: \n508: ## Error Handling\n509: \n510: ### Workflow Failure Categories\n511: \n512: | Category | Description | Recovery Action |\n513: |----------|-------------|-----------------|\n514: | `BuildFailure` | Docker build or compilation error | Log output, fail job |\n515: | `LintFailure` | golangci-lint or Ruff violations | Report violations, fail job |\n516: | `TestFailure` | Unit test or E2E test failure | Upload artifacts, fail job |\n517: | `CodegenDrift` | Generated code differs from committed | Show diff, fail job |\n518: | `CopyrightDrift` | Copyright headers mismatch | Show diff, fail job |\n519: | `SpellingError` | codespell detected typos | Report errors, fail job |\n520: | `RegistryAuthFailure` | Docker login failed | Log error, fail job |\n521: | `KindSetupFailure` | Kind cluster creation failed | Upload logs, fail job |\n522: | `CoverageUploadFailure` | Codecov upload failed | Continue (non-blocking) |\n523: \n524: ### Conditional Failure Handling\n525: \n526: ```yaml\n527: failure_handling:\n528:   e2e_failure:\n529:     if: failure()\n530:     steps:\n531:       - name: Upload E2E logs\n532:         uses: actions/upload-artifact@v4\n533:         with:\n534:           name: e2e-logs\n535:           path: e2e-logs/\n536:   \n537:   e2e_cleanup:\n538:     if: always()\n539:     steps:\n540:       - name: Cleanup E2E\n541:         run: make e2e-clean\n542:         continue-on-error: true\n543:   \n544:   coverage_upload:\n545:     if: success()\n546:     steps:\n547:       - name: Upload to Codecov\n548:         uses: codecov/codecov-action@v4\n549:         with:\n550:           fail_ci_if_error: false\n551: ```\n552: \n553: ### Path Filter Skip Logic\n554: \n555: ```yaml\n556: path_filter_skip:\n557:   pattern: |\n558:     if: steps.filter.outputs.<filter-name> != 'true'\n559:     run: echo \"No <filter-name> changes detected, skipping job\"\n560:     \n561:   skip_job: |\n562:     jobs:\n563:       <job-name>:\n564:         if: ${{ needs.<previous-job>.outputs.<filter-name> == 'true' }}\n565: ```\n566: \n567: ### Secrets Handling\n568: \n569: ```yaml\n570: secrets_contract:\n571:   GITHUB_TOKEN:\n572:     scope: write (for gh pr create)\n573:     usage: Registry login, GitHub API\n574:     built_in: true\n575:   \n576:   CODECOV_TOKEN:\n577:     scope: read\n578:     usage: Codecov upload authentication\n579:     optional: true\n580:     declared_in: workflow_call\n581:     \n582:   PLUGIN_ACTION:\n583:     scope: write (for cross-repo checkout and PR)\n584:     usage: Dify plugin publish workflow\n585:     required_for: dify-plugin-publish.yml\n586: ```\n587: \n588: ### Timeout Configuration\n589: \n590: ```yaml\n591: timeout_config:\n592:   job_timeout:\n593:     default: 30m\n594:     e2e: 45m\n595:     \n596:   step_timeout:\n597:     go_test: 10m\n598:     e2e_run: 30m\n599:     docker_build: 15m\n600:     docker_push: 20m\n601: ```\n602: \n603: ---\n604: \n605: ## Testing Strategy\n606: \n607: ### Workflow Validation Matrix\n608: \n609: | Workflow | Validation Method | Test Command |\n610: |----------|-------------------|--------------|\n611: | `main.yml` | Docker build success | `make docker-build` |\n612: | `e2e.yml` | E2E test execution | `make e2e` in Kind cluster |\n613: | `lint.yml` | golangci-lint pass | `make lint` |\n614: | `python-sdk-tests.yml` | pytest pass | `python -m pytest tests/ -v` |\n615: | `python-lint.yml` | Ruff pass | `ruff check . --config pyproject.toml` |\n616: | `test-coverage.yml` | Coverage generation | `go test -race -coverprofile=coverage.out ./pkg/...` |\n617: | `codegen-check.yml` | No drift | `make gen-check && git diff --exit-code` |\n618: | `copyright-check.yml` | No drift | `make gen-copyright && git diff --exit-code` |\n619: | `codespell.yml` | No spelling errors | `codespell --check-filenames .` |\n620: | `build-push-release.yml` | Registry push | `make docker-buildx-push` (with registry auth) |\n621: | `dify-plugin-publish.yml` | Plugin package | `dify-plugin package` |\n622: | `workflows-approve.yml` | API approval | GitHub API `approveWorkflowRun` |\n623: \n624: ### E2E Test Sequence\n625: \n626: ```yaml\n627: e2e_test_sequence:\n628:   setup:\n629:     - name: Create Kind cluster\n630:       command: kind create cluster --name agentcube-e2e\n631:     \n632:     - name: Load images\n633:       command: kind load docker-image <image-list>\n634:     \n635:     - name: Apply CRDs\n636:       command: kubectl apply --validate=false -f <crd-urls>\n637:     \n638:     - name: Install Helm chart\n639:       command: helm upgrade --install agentcube manifests/charts/base\n640:     \n641:     - name: Port-forward services\n642:       command: kubectl port-forward svc/<service>\n643:     \n644:     - name: Health check\n645:       command: curl http://localhost:<port>/health\n646:     \n647:   test_execution:\n648:     - name: Go E2E tests\n649:       env:\n650:         WORKLOAD_MANAGER_URL: http://localhost:8080\n651:         ROUTER_URL: http://localhost:8081\n652:         API_TOKEN: <generated-token>\n653:       command: go test -v ./test/e2e/...\n654:     \n655:     - name: Python E2E tests\n656:       command: python test_codeinterpreter.py\n657:     \n658:   cleanup:\n659:     - name: Delete Kind cluster\n660:       command: kind delete cluster --name agentcube-e2e\n661:       if: always()\n662:     \n663:     - name: Remove temp files\n664:       command: rm -rf /tmp/agent-sandbox\n665:       if: always()\n666: ```\n667: \n668: ### Coverage Test Specification\n669: \n670: ```yaml\n671: coverage_test_spec:\n672:   command: |\n673:     go test -race -v \\\n674:       -coverprofile=coverage.out \\\n675:       -coverpkg=./pkg/... \\\n676:       ./pkg/...\n677:   \n678:   package_scope: ./pkg/...\n679:   \n680:   race_detector: enabled\n681:   \n682:   output:\n683:     coverage.out: coverage profile\n684:     step_summary: coverage percentage\n685:   \n686:   upload:\n687:     provider: Codecov\n688:     file: coverage.out\n689:     fail_on_error: false\n690: ```\n691: \n692: ### Python Test Specification\n693: \n694: ```yaml\n695: python_test_spec:\n696:   sdk_tests:\n697:     working_directory: sdk-python\n698:     python_version: '3.12'\n699:     setup:\n700:       - pip install pytest\n701:       - pip install -e .\n702:     command: python -m pytest tests/ -v\n703:   \n704:   e2e_python:\n705:     working_directory: test/e2e\n706:     python_version: '3.12'\n707:     venv: /tmp/agentcube-e2e-venv\n708:     setup:\n709:       - python3 -m venv $E2E_VENV_DIR\n710:       - pip install -e ./sdk-python\n711:     command: python test_codeinterpreter.py\n712: ```\n713: \n714: ### Workflow Self-Test Commands\n715: \n716: ```yaml\n717: workflow_self_test:\n718:   validate_yaml:\n719:     command: yamllint .github/workflows/*.yml\n720:     \n721:   check_syntax:\n722:     command: gh workflow view <workflow-name>\n723:     \n724:   test_trigger:\n725:     command: gh workflow run <workflow-name> --ref <branch>\n726:     \n727:   verify_artifacts:\n728:     command: gh run download <run-id>\n729: ```\n730: \n731: ---\n732: \n733: ## File Structure\n734: \n735: ```\n736: .github/\n737: ├── workflows/\n738: │   ├── main.yml                    # PR Docker build verification\n739: │   ├── e2e.yml                     # E2E tests on Kind\n740: │   ├── lint.yml                    # Go lint with path filter\n741: │   ├── python-sdk-tests.yml        # Python SDK pytest\n742: │   ├── python-lint.yml             # Python Ruff lint\n743: │   ├── test-coverage.yml           # Go coverage + Codecov\n744: │   ├── codegen-check.yml           # Generated code drift\n745: │   ├── copyright-check.yml         # Copyright header check\n746: │   ├── codespell.yml               # Spelling verification\n747: │   ├── build-push-release.yml      # Multi-arch image push\n748: │   ├── dify-plugin-publish.yml     # Dify plugin release\n749: │   └── workflows-approve.yml       # Auto-approve trusted\n750: └── filters.yaml                    # (optional) Centralized path filters\n751: ```\n752: \n753: ### Workflow File Size Estimates\n754: \n755: | Workflow | Estimated Lines | Complexity |\n756: |----------|-----------------|------------|\n757: | `main.yml` | ~30 | Low |\n758: | `e2e.yml` | ~80 | High |\n759: | `lint.yml` | ~50 | Medium |\n760: | `python-sdk-tests.yml` | ~40 | Low |\n761: | `python-lint.yml` | ~50 | Medium |\n762: | `test-coverage.yml` | ~60 | Medium |\n763: | `codegen-check.yml` | ~50 | Medium |\n764: | `copyright-check.yml` | ~50 | Medium |\n765: | `codespell.yml` | ~80 | Medium |\n766: | `build-push-release.yml` | ~100 | High |\n767: | `dify-plugin-publish.yml` | ~120 | High |\n768: | `workflows-approve.yml` | ~70 | High |\n769: \n770: ---\n771: \n772: ## Dependencies\n773: \n774: ### GitHub Actions Dependencies\n775: \n776: | Action | Version | Purpose |\n777: |--------|---------|---------|\n778: | `actions/checkout` | v4 | Repository checkout with history |\n779: | `actions/setup-go` | v5 | Go toolchain (versions 1.23, 1.24, 1.24.4) |\n780: | `actions/setup-python` | v5 | Python toolchain (versions 3.10, 3.12) |\n781: | `docker/setup-buildx-action` | v3 | Docker Buildx setup |\n782: | `docker/login-action` | v3 | Container registry authentication |\n783: | `helm/kind-action` | v1 | Kind cluster tooling (v0.30.0) |\n784: | `dorny/paths-filter` | v3 | Path-based job filtering |\n785: | `codecov/codecov-action` | v4 | Coverage report upload |\n786: | `actions/upload-artifact` | v4 | Artifact storage |\n787: | `actions/github-script` | v7 | GitHub API scripting |\n788: \n789: ### Tool Dependencies\n790: \n791: | Tool | Version | Purpose |\n792: |------|---------|---------|\n793: | Go | 1.23, 1.24, 1.24.4 | Go builds and tests |\n794: | Python | 3.10, 3.12 | Python lint and SDK tests |\n795: | Docker | latest | Container builds |\n796: | Buildx | latest | Multi-architecture builds |\n797: | Kind | v0.30.0 | Kubernetes in Docker |\n798: | golangci-lint | (project default) | Go linting |\n799: | Ruff | latest | Python linting |\n800: | pytest | latest | Python testing |\n801: | codespell | latest | Spelling check |\n802: | yq | latest | YAML processing (dify-plugin) |\n803: | dify-plugin CLI | 0.0.6 | Plugin packaging |\n804: \n805: ### External Resources\n806: \n807: | Resource | URL | Purpose |\n808: |----------|-----|---------|\n809: | agent-sandbox CRDs | github.com/kubernetes-sigs/agent-sandbox/releases | Kind cluster setup |\n810: | agent-sandbox controller | registry.k8s.io/agent-sandbox | E2E dependencies |\n811: | python:3.9-slim | Docker Hub | Echo agent workload |\n812: | redis:7-alpine | Docker Hub | Session store |\n813: | ghcr.io | GitHub Container Registry | Image publication |\n814: | Codecov | codecov.com | Coverage reporting |\n815: | dify-plugins repo | github.com/langgenius/dify-plugins | Plugin publication |\n816: \n817: ---\n818: \n819: ## Implementation Notes\n820: \n821: ### Workflow Naming Convention\n822: \n823: - Filenames: lowercase with hyphens (e.g., `main.yml`, `e2e.yml`)\n824: - Workflow `name`: descriptive titles (e.g., \"Agentcube CI Workflow\")\n825: - Job names: descriptive with underscores (e.g., `build`, `e2e-test`, `coverage`)\n826: - Step names: action-oriented descriptions\n827: \n828: ### Path Filter Pattern\n829: \n830: - Use `dorny/paths-filter@v3` for all path-sensitive workflows\n831: - Filters defined inline or in separate `filters.yaml` file\n832: - Output used in `if:` conditions for job skipping\n833: - Inverted patterns (`!*.md`) for exclusion\n834: \n835: ### Kind Cluster Isolation\n836: \n837: - Use `install_only: true` to prevent `helm/kind-action` from creating cluster\n838: - Cluster name: `agentcube-e2e`\n839: - Cleanup in `always()` block to ensure resource release\n840: - Logs collected in `ARTIFACTS_PATH` on failure\n841: \n842: ### Registry Authentication\n843: \n844: - Use `GITHUB_TOKEN` (built-in) for `ghcr.io` authentication\n845: - No long-lived secrets required for main workflow\n846: - `PLUGIN_ACTION` secret for cross-repo operations in dify-plugin workflow\n847: \n848: ### Coverage Upload Strategy\n849: \n850: - Upload `coverage.out` as artifact first\n851: - Codecov upload is non-blocking (`fail_ci_if_error: false`)\n852: - `CODECOV_TOKEN` optional via `workflow_call` secrets\n853: \n854: ### First-time Contributor Handling\n855: \n856: - Use `pull_request_target` for access to repo secrets\n857: - Check contributor PR count via GitHub API\n858: - Approve `action_required` workflow runs for trusted contributors\n859: - `ok-to-test` label overrides first-time check\n860: \n861: ---\n862: \n863: ## References\n864: \n865: - Spec: `changes/AR-034/spec.md`\n866: - Delta Spec: `changes/AR-034/delta-spec.md`\n867: - Proposal: `changes/AR-034/proposal.md`\n868: - Tasks: `changes/AR-034/tasks.md`\n869: - CI/CD Reference: `ci-cd/design.md`\n870: - CI/CD Specification: `ci-cd/spec.md`\n871: - E2E Test Script: `test/e2e/run_e2e.sh`\n872: - Makefile: `Makefile`\n873: - GitHub Actions Docs: https://docs.github.com/en/actions\n874: - Kind Docs: https://kind.sigs.k8s.io/\n875: - Docker Buildx: https://docs.docker.com/buildx/working-with-buildx/\n\n(End of file - total 875 lines)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"# AR-034 — CI/CD GitHub Actions Design\n\n## Overview\n\n| Item | Value |\n|------|-------|\n| AR | AR-034 — CI/CD GitHub Actions (12 workflows) |\n| Module | `.github` |\n| Language | YAML |\n| Size | L |\n| Stage | ST-1 (completed) |\n\n---\n\n## Architecture\n\n### High-Level CI/CD Pipeline Flow\n\n```\n┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐","truncated":false,"loaded":[]},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20260410T163124Z/changes/AR-034/design.md","time":{"start":1775889359227,"end":1775889359242}}}}
