{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775889580723,"sessionID":"ses_284bf8cc4ffepOzrBWJCfD7y2y","part":{"id":"prt_d7b44811400159XaJ2GZaMk0jR","messageID":"msg_d7b4121b8001brb4lF7Y20QY9V","sessionID":"ses_284bf8cc4ffepOzrBWJCfD7y2y","type":"tool","tool":"write","callID":"toolu_tool-c9326b3e0ac345cdb5f00677c7af1e51","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20260410T163124Z/changes/AR-034/tasks.md","content":"# AR-034 — CI/CD GitHub Actions Tasks\n\n## Metadata\n\n| Item | Value |\n|------|-------|\n| AR | AR-034 — CI/CD GitHub Actions (12 workflows) |\n| Module | `.github` |\n| Language | YAML |\n| Size | L |\n| Design | [Stage ST-3 completed] |\n\n---\n\n## Task Checklist\n\n### Phase 1: Directory Structure Setup (ST-1)\n\n- [ ] **T1.1**: Create `.github/` directory\n  - Purpose: Initialize GitHub configuration directory\n  - File: `.github/`\n  - Verification: `test -d .github`\n\n- [ ] **T1.2**: Create `.github/workflows/` directory\n  - Purpose: Initialize workflows directory\n  - File: `.github/workflows/`\n  - Verification: `test -d .github/workflows`\n\n### Phase 2: main.yml - PR Docker Build (ST-2)\n\n- [ ] **T2.1**: Create workflow file `.github/workflows/main.yml`\n  - Purpose: Initialize main CI workflow file\n  - File: `.github/workflows/main.yml`\n  - Verification: `test -f .github/workflows/main.yml`\n\n- [ ] **T2.2**: Add workflow name \"Agentcube CI Workflow\"\n  - Purpose: Define workflow display name\n  - File: `.github/workflows/main.yml`\n  - Verification: `grep \"name: Agentcube CI Workflow\" .github/workflows/main.yml`\n\n- [ ] **T2.3**: Add `on: pull_request` trigger for main and release branches\n  - Purpose: Trigger on PR to main/release branches\n  - File: `.github/workflows/main.yml`\n  - Verification: `grep \"pull_request:\" .github/workflows/main.yml && grep \"main\" .github/workflows/main.yml`\n\n- [ ] **T2.4**: Add `on: push` trigger for main branch\n  - Purpose: Trigger on push to main\n  - File: `.github/workflows/main.yml`\n  - Verification: `grep \"push:\" .github/workflows/main.yml`\n\n- [ ] **T2.5**: Define `build` job with `runs-on: ubuntu-latest`\n  - Purpose: Set runner environment\n  - File: `.github/workflows/main.yml`\n  - Verification: `grep \"runs-on: ubuntu-latest\" .github/workflows/main.yml`\n\n- [ ] **T2.6**: Add `actions/checkout@v4` step\n  - Purpose: Checkout repository code\n  - File: `.github/workflows/main.yml`\n  - Verification: `grep \"uses: actions/checkout@v4\" .github/workflows/main.yml`\n\n- [ ] **T2.7**: Add `docker/setup-buildx-action@v3` step\n  - Purpose: Configure Docker Buildx\n  - File: `.github/workflows/main.yml`\n  - Verification: `grep \"uses: docker/setup-buildx-action@v3\" .github/workflows/main.yml`\n\n- [ ] **T2.8**: Add `make docker-build` step\n  - Purpose: Build workloadmanager Docker image\n  - File: `.github/workflows/main.yml`\n  - Verification: `grep \"make docker-build\" .github/workflows/main.yml`\n\n### Phase 3: lint.yml - Go Lint with Path Filter (ST-3)\n\n- [ ] **T3.1**: Create workflow file `.github/workflows/lint.yml`\n  - Purpose: Initialize lint workflow file\n  - File: `.github/workflows/lint.yml`\n  - Verification: `test -f .github/workflows/lint.yml`\n\n- [ ] **T3.2**: Add workflow name \"Go Lint\"\n  - Purpose: Define workflow display name\n  - File: `.github/workflows/lint.yml`\n  - Verification: `grep \"name: Go Lint\" .github/workflows/lint.yml`\n\n- [ ] **T3.3**: Add `on: pull_request` trigger for main branch\n  - Purpose: Trigger on PR to main\n  - File: `.github/workflows/lint.yml`\n  - Verification: `grep \"pull_request:\" .github/workflows/lint.yml`\n\n- [ ] **T3.4**: Define `filter` job with `dorny/paths-filter@v3`\n  - Purpose: Detect Go file changes\n  - File: `.github/workflows/lint.yml`\n  - Verification: `grep \"uses: dorny/paths-filter@v3\" .github/workflows/lint.yml`\n\n- [ ] **T3.5**: Add path filter for `lint: ['**/*.go', 'go.mod', 'go.sum