thon-sdk-tests.yml` runs pytest in sdk-python directory\n- [ ] `python-lint.yml` runs Ruff with `pyproject.toml` config\n- [ ] `e2e.yml` creates Kind cluster named `agentcube-e2e`\n- [ ] `e2e.yml` has cleanup in `if: always()` block\n- [ ] `e2e.yml` uploads logs on failure\n- [ ] `build-push-release.yml` triggers on `v*` tags\n- [ ] `build-push-release.yml` builds multi-arch (linux/amd64, linux/arm64)\n- [ ] `build-push-release.yml` pushes to ghcr.io\n- [ ] `dify-plugin-publish.yml` triggers on `dify-plugin/v*` tags\n- [ ] `dify-plugin-publish.yml` creates PR to `langgenius/dify-plugins`\n- [ ] `workflows-approve.yml` uses `pull_request_target` for secrets access\n- [ ] `workflows-approve.yml` checks `ok-to-test` label\n- [ ] `filters.yaml` defines all 6 filter categories (lint, sdk, python, coverage, codegen, copyright)\n- [ ] All workflows use consistent action versions (checkout@v4, setup-go@v5, setup-python@v5)\n- [ ] All workflow files have valid YAML syntax\n- [ ] All workflow filenames follow lowercase-hyphen naming convention\n\n---\n\n## File Changes Summary\n\n| File | Action | Lines | Description |\n|------|--------|-------|-------------|\n| `.github/` | Create | - | GitHub configuration directory |\n| `.github/workflows/` | Create | - | Workflows directory |\n| `.github/workflows/main.yml` | Create | ~30 | PR Docker build verification |\n| `.github/workflows/lint.yml` | Create | ~50 | Go lint with path filter |\n| `.github/workflows/test-coverage.yml` | Create | ~60 | Go coverage + Codecov |\n| `.github/workflows/codegen-check.yml` | Create | ~50 | Generated code drift check |\n| `.github/workflows/copyright-check.yml` | Create | ~50 | Copyright header check |\n| `.github/workflows/codespell.yml` | Create | ~80 | Spelling verification |\n| `.github/workflows/python-sdk-tests.yml` | Create | ~40 | Python SDK pytest |\n| `.github/workflows/python-lint.yml` | Create | ~50 | Python Ruff lint |\n| `.github/workflows/e2e.yml` | Create | ~80 | E2E tests on Kind